metadata.name: Bored Mummy #1
metadata.description: BoredMummyWakingUp is a collection of 8,888 unique BoredMummy NFTs- digital collectibles living on the Ethereum Blockchain. Summon the legends that seal by powerful magic from the Divine Chronosphere. “When the New Moon Begins, King Tide Arise Only the Chosen one can awaken the Book of Death, where the summoning begin…” BMWU is one of the kind NFT you must have in your wallet, own a guardian and choose the realm you believe in. Future activations and perks will be unlocked by the community through roadmap activation. For more info about BoredMummyWakingUp, visit - www.boredmummywakingup.com
